  "instructions": [
    "Rinse quinoa, farro, and brown rice under cold water.",
    "In a pressure cooker, combine rinsed grains with vegetable broth and umami seasoning. Cook according to manufacturer's instructions until done.",
    "Sauté minced garlic in a pan over medium heat until fragrant, add shiitake mushrooms, and sauté for another 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add snow peas to the pan and cook for an additional minute or two until heated through.",
    "Toss cooked grains with prepared vegetables and sauce (if using). Serve hot.",
    "Optional: Drizzle a bit of fish sauce over the top if desired."
